column5: We are into the home stretch of our auction for Rick. The auction will close on Saturday the 13th at midnight. There are some great offerings and still more being added. Please have a look HERE!  Thanks folks. Everyone's participation is greatly appreciated.

If I kicked ya in the butt,would you get TTT?  Lets see Kick  Yep it worked,even from way over here.LOL  I too would like to say thanks to all that have bid and helpped our friend.  Good job done by all.
